The '''Ministry of Health''' is a [[government ministry]] that governs and manages [[healthcare]] and the [[health|health industry]] in [[Tajikistan]], including the nation's [[public health]] system. The Ministry was founded in 2006 and is located in [[Dushanbe]].<ref>[http://www.health.tj/en/ Ministry, Front page]</ref>
